    "body": "I like the idea, but :-1: for having this as a default part of the engine. Orders are meant to be a code-level abstraction not seen by the user, and creating & managing them properly in a use case like this will probably be a pain.\n\nEDIT: maybe we can have a little bit more customization over the controls and allow for special macros, but I don't think exposing orders to the user is a good idea.\n"
